A simple first-person shooter for the Nintendo DS

This will be made iteratively and new builds available via:
https://ci.opengamedevelopers.org

Lastest builds can be downloaded from:
ftp://ftp.opengamedevelopers.org/projects/zds/builds/unstable/latest
ftp://ftp.opengamedevelopers.org/projects/zds/builds/stable/latest

The stable builds are as bug-free as possible, while unstable will have as many 
bugs as the new features implemented accrue.
